18 with alcoholic beverages shall not be included in this prohibition,
19 but no wholesaler or retailer shall sell any alcoholic beverage
20 prepackaged with other goods or merchandise at a price which is
21 greater than the price at which the alcoholic beverage alone is
22 sold; provided, it shall not be considered inducement or a premium
23 for a retail spirits licensee to have an advertised price posted
24 higher online than the shelf price on the licensed premises; or
